<i>♪ I feel all right ♪</i>

24:13.653 --> 24:16.387
<i>♪ I'm gonna take on the world ♪</i>

24:16.389 --> 24:17.621
<i>♪ Light up the stars ♪</i>

24:17.623 --> 24:19.657
<i>♪ I've got</i>
<i>some pages to turn ♪</i>

24:19.659 --> 24:21.926
<i>♪ I'm singing "Go-o-o" ♪</i>

24:21.928 --> 24:24.495
<i>♪ Oh, oh, oh, oh ♪</i>

24:24.497 --> 24:27.798
<i>♪ Take on the world,</i>
<i>take on the world ♪</i>

24:27.800 --> 24:30.001
<i>♪ Take on the world ♪</i>

